pidgin-whatsapp (0.8) trusty; urgency=low

  * Ability to change profile picture
  * Ability to set privacy options
  * Fixed image sending by creating realistic thumbnails
  * Fixed profile picture update for contacts in buddy list
  * Fixing some features to look like an android phone
  * Supports receiving broadcast messages
  * Fixed some minor bugs with groups and some cleanup
  * Fixed some leaks (probably some still ther)
  * Fixing status message setting
  * Fixed photo thumbnails display when receiving media messages

 -- David Guillen Fandos <david@davidgf.net>  Sun, 22 Mar 2015 23:23:00 +0100

